            . I superintend my my mother-in-law's business, Elizabeth Dodd - she <rs id="t18311201-190-viclabel1017" type="occupation">keeps <placeName id="t18311201-190-crimeloc1018">the Ship, in Sun Tavern-fields</placeName>
                     <interp inst="t18311201-190-crimeloc1018" type="placeName" value="the Ship, in Sun Tavern-fields"></interp>
